https://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/PressReleases/Pages/statistics-2018-04-10-001.aspx

4- Registered on 9 Apr 2018: no information available.

5- Reported on 8 Apr 2018: A 58-year-old Saudi male from Najran [Najran region] with a history of pre-existing co-morbidities [reported as a newly confirmed case on 2 Apr 2018 at which time he was noted to be in stable condition [see newly confirmed case no. 6 above. Classified as a primary case with high risk exposure history still under investigation. - Mod.MPP]
https://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/PressReleases/Pages/statistics-2018-04-08-001.aspx

6- Reported on 4 Apr 2018: A 62-year old Saudi female from Median [Al Madinah region] with a history of pre-existing co-morbidities [reported as a newly confirmed case on 20 Mar 2018 at which time she was noted to be in stable condition. Classified as a primary case with high risk exposure history still under investigation. - Mod.MPP]
