7- Reported on 4 Apr 2018: A 54-year-old Saudi male from Hufoof [Ash Sharq朝yah - Eastern region] with a history of pre-existing co-morbidities [reported as a newly confirmed case on 30 Mar 2018 at which time he was noted to be in stable condition. Classified as a primary case with a history of direct contact with camels. - Mod.MPP]
https://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/PressReleases/Pages/statistics-2018-04-04-001.aspx

