https://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/PressReleases/Pages/statistics-2018-04-02-001.aspx

9- Reported on 2 Apr 2018: A 39-year-old Saudi female from Jeddah [Makkah region] with no history of co-morbidities [reported as a newly confirmed case on 14 Mar 2018 at which time she was noted to be in stable condition. Classified as a secondary case in a household contact. - Mod.MPP]
https://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/PressReleases/Pages/statistics-2018-04-02-001.aspx

